---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Pricing"
  description="BharatDCIM pricing starts at Rs.500/rack/month. Simple, transparent pricing for Indian data center operators. Up to 85% below global DCIM incumbents."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="section-label">Pricing</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Enterprise DCIM at<br />
          <span class="text-[--color-accent]">Indian Pricing</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Simple per-rack pricing. No hidden fees, no surprise connector costs.
          Up to 85% below global DCIM incumbents.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Tiers -->
  <section class="section pt-0">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Starter -->
        <div class="card border-2 border-gray-100">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Starter</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">For smaller facilities</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Rs.500</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">/rack/month</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">10-50 racks</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Asset tracking and inventory
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Tenant management
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Basic power billing
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Email support
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary w-full justify-center text-sm py-3">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Professional - Highlighted -->
        <div class="card border-2 border-[--color-accent] relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="bg-[--color-accent] text-white text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Most Popular</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Professional</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">For growing operations</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Rs.800</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">/rack/month</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">50-200 racks</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Everything in Starter
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              <strong>ToD billing engine</strong> with state-specific tariffs
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Real-time power monitoring
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              SLA tracking and reporting
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              <strong>GST-compliant invoicing</strong> (SAC 998315)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Priority support
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary w-full justify-center text-sm py-3">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Enterprise -->
        <div class="card border-2 border-gray-100">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Enterprise</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">For large-scale operations</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Rs.1,200</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">/rack/month</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">200+ racks</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Everything in Professional
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              <strong>Multi-site management</strong>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              REST API access
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              White-label tenant portal
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
              Dedicated account manager
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary w-full justify-center text-sm py-3">Contact Sales</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Volume Discounts -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-16">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">Volume Discounts</h3>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-primary]">17%</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Annual billing discount</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-primary]">10%</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">500+ racks</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-primary]">15%</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">1,000+ racks</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Competitor Comparison -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="section-label">Comparison</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          How We Compare to<br />
          <span class="accent">Global Incumbents</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
          <table class="w-full">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <th class="text-left p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Feature</th>
                <th class="text-center p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-[--color-accent]">BharatDCIM</th>
                <th class="text-center p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400">Nlyte</th>
                <th class="text-center p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400">Sunbird</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-50">
                <td class="p-4 text-sm text-gray-700">Cost for 100 racks</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-green-600">~Rs.80K/month</span>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">~$100K+ setup</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">$49K-70K perpetual</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-50">
                <td class="p-4 text-sm text-gray-700">Indian ToD tariffs</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-50">
                <td class="p-4 text-sm text-gray-700">GST-compliant invoicing</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-50">
                <td class="p-4 text-sm text-gray-700">DG power tracking</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center text-xs text-gray-400">Add-on</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center text-xs text-gray-400">Manual</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-50">
                <td class="p-4 text-sm text-gray-700">kWh and kVAh billing</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-4 text-sm text-gray-700">Setup time</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center text-sm font-medium text-green-600">Days</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">Months</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">Weeks</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Common<br />
          <span class="accent">Questions</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is there a free trial?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Yes. We offer a 14-day free trial with full access to all Professional tier features.
            No credit card required to start.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What happens if my rack count changes?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Billing adjusts automatically. If you add racks mid-month, you're billed pro-rata.
            If you decommission racks, the next month reflects the lower count.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you charge for GST invoicing?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            GST-compliant invoicing is included in the Professional and Enterprise tiers at no extra cost.
            This includes proper SAC codes (998315), GSTIN validation, and e-invoice JSON export.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I switch tiers later?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            You can upgrade or downgrade at any time. Changes take effect at the start of your
            next billing cycle. Annual subscribers can upgrade mid-term with pro-rated pricing.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What about the early access program?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Our first 10 customers receive founding member pricing (up to 50% off), direct access
            to the engineering team, and priority feature requests.
            <a href="/contact" class="text-[--color-primary] hover:underline">Apply for early access</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section bg-[--color-primary] text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
          Ready to Modernize Your Billing?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10">
          Start with a free trial or schedule a demo to see BharatDCIM in action.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-light text-lg px-8 py-4">Schedule Demo</a>
          <a href="/calculator" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-lg text-white/90 hover:text-white">
            Try Calculator <span>â†’</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
